== 製作 ==
在電影的概念化過程中，[[艾瑞克·安德烈|艾瑞克·安德烈]]參加了[[罗伯特·麦基|罗伯特·麦基]]的故事研討會，並諮詢了喜劇演員{{le|傑夫·崔曼|Jeff Tremaine}}和{{le|納森·菲爾德|Nathan Fielder}}。影片製作完成後，安德烈將片子給他們及[[薩夏·拜倫·柯恩|薩夏·拜倫·柯恩]]觀賞，柯恩是隱藏鏡頭整人和電影的資深人士。<ref name="esquire">{{Cite web |title=Eric Andre On the Penis Prank That Almost Got Him Shot and the Return of His Beloved Show |url=https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/tv/a28437590/eric-andre-interview-show-season-five-pranking-bad-trip-lion-king/ |last=Nero |first=Dom |date=2019-07-19 |website=Esquire |access-date=2019-07-29 |archive-date=2019-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728123951/https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/tv/a28437590/eric-andre-interview-show-season-five-pranking-bad-trip-lion-king/}}</ref>

